    <item>
      <title>战争持续，泽连斯基“不惧怕”特朗普新总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/zelenskiy-not-afraid-of-new-trump-presidency-as-war-drags-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，他“并不害怕”唐纳德·特朗普可能再次担任总统，尽管他表示美国大选的动荡正在损害基辅在战场上的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/zelenskiy-not-afraid-of-new-trump-presidency-as-war-drags-on</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 14:21:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佛罗里达州法官驳回特朗普机密文件案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-classified-documents-case-dismissed-by-florida-judge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官驳回了针对唐纳德·特朗普处理机密信息不当的刑事案件，并认定特别顾问杰克·史密斯的任命违宪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-classified-documents-case-dismissed-by-florida-judge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 13:55:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普为袭击受害者筹款活动 GoFundMe 筹集 300 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-campaign-gofundme-for-victims-of-attack-raises-3-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普竞选团队发起了一项 GoFundMe 活动，旨在帮助周六晚间疑似暗杀事件的受害者及其家属，目前该活动已从 50,000 多笔捐款中筹集到 350 多万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-campaign-gofundme-for-victims-of-attack-raises-3-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 13:49:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党希望抓住威斯康星州选民对经济的悲观看法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/gop-to-use-wisconsin-voters-economic-concerns-at-rnc-election-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[威斯康星州的经济目前状况良好。然而，那里的选民表示，他们担心明天的经济状况会如何——唐纳德·特朗普希望他能利用这种焦虑击败总统乔·拜登。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/gop-to-use-wisconsin-voters-economic-concerns-at-rnc-election-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 13:40:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国和欧盟将对俄罗斯石油船队实施更多检查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/uk-eu-states-to-target-russian-oil-fleet-with-more-checks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士和彭博社看到的文件显示，英国计划本周与一些欧洲国家一起发起“行动呼吁”，针对俄罗斯用来规避国际制裁的所谓“影子油轮舰队”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/uk-eu-states-to-target-russian-oil-fleet-with-more-checks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 13:32:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>危机谈判进展不明朗 肯尼亚准备迎接更多抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/kenya-braces-for-more-protests-with-crisis-talks-status-unclear</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托提出的帮助结束该国政治危机的谈判似乎陷入停滞，肯尼亚准备迎接更多的反政府抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/kenya-braces-for-more-protests-with-crisis-talks-status-unclear</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 12:55:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>审计人员称法国解决“令人担忧”财政问题的计划缺乏可信度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/french-audit-court-says-deficit-gap-versus-eu-is-unacceptable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国国家审计长表示，现有的修复“令人担忧”的公共财政的计划缺乏可信度，这为预算敲响了警钟，因为持有扩张性税收和支出政策的政治团体正争相在提前选举后组建新政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/french-audit-court-says-deficit-gap-versus-eu-is-unacceptable</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 06:15:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普枪击事件后，美国特勤局面临严格审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-secret-service-faces-intense-scrutiny-after-trump-shooting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普遭暗杀事件发生后，美国特勤局这个有着不光彩过去的机构被推到了政治风暴的中心，正面临公众的严厉审查和调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-secret-service-faces-intense-scrutiny-after-trump-shooting</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 21:53:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球市场在反弹后“特朗普交易”增多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/global-markets-ramp-up-the-trump-trade-after-rally-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普遇刺未遂之后，世界金融市场重新开放，有一件事很明显：特朗普交易正在获得动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/global-markets-ramp-up-the-trump-trade-after-rally-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
